title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Sim Update 6 - What to expect
description:
Asobo will release Sim Update VI early next if everything goes well. Currently the update is being validated by beta testers which subscribed to the beta testing program. In this video we will have a look on which fixed to expect in the next Sim Update which is scheduled to be available on the 19th of October.
